title: GTA Online
headline: GTA Online
subtitle: The Överflöd Suzume Supercar
content:
The Överflöd Suzume (Super) spent most of its life shrouded in secrecy. First as a classified sketch, then as a super-limited concept car, and now it’s finally unleashed upon the general populace in all its glory.

Join the vanguard by purchasing one from Legendary Motorsport.
